text: Gonzalo Ezequiel Rodriguez (born 4 October 1997 in Buenos Aires) is an Argentine professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for Club Atlético Velez Sarsfield. Rodriguez made his debut for Velez Sarsfield in the Argentine Primera División on April 21, 2018 against Temperley coming on a substitute for Mauro Zárate. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Sportspeople from Buenos Aires Category:Argentine footballers Category:Argentine Primera División players Category:Club Atlético Vélez Sarsfield footballers Category:Association football midfielders
